* text=auto eol=lf

*.blade.php diff=html
*.css diff=css
*.html diff=html
*.md diff=markdown
*.php diff=php

### Binary file handling ###
# Images
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.webp binary
*.bmp binary

# Documents
*.pdf binary
*.doc binary
*.docx binary
*.xls binary
*.xlsx binary
*.ppt binary
*.pptx binary

# Archives
*.zip binary
*.gz binary
*.tar binary
*.rar binary
*.7z binary

# Fonts
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.eot binary
*.otf binary

### Export-ignore (excluded from git archive) ###
/.github export-ignore
/tests export-ignore
.gitattributes export-ignore
.gitignore export-ignore
.editorconfig export-ignore
CONTRIBUTING.md export-ignore
CHANGELOG.md export-ignore
phpunit.xml export-ignore
.styleci.yml export-ignore
